  <brief_title>Mass Spectral Fingerprinting in Obstructive Sleep Apnoea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Diagnosis of Obstructive Sleep Apnoea by Selective Secondary Electrospray Ionization - Mass Spectrometry (SESIMS)</official_title>
