  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To answer the question whether a previously detected breath profile in patients suffering
      from obstructive sleep apnoea (OSA) can be found in a cohort of patients with suspected OSA
      using mass spectrometry (validation study).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
